  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game where you can learn about chopsticks while challenging physics-based puzzles with handling chopsticks. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up and move food from plate to plate with chopsticks to solve puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The movement of chopsticks are accurately based on physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various types of chopsticks are available in game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no known correlation between performing well in the game and improving actual chopstick skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.poster.avif?t=1771035517\" width=426 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.webm?t=1771035517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.mp4?t=1771035517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is inspired by the game below:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game where you can learn about chopsticks while challenging physics-based puzzles with handling chopsticks. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up and move food from plate to plate with chopsticks to solve puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The movement of chopsticks are accurately based on physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various types of chopsticks are available in game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no known correlation between performing well in the game and improving actual chopstick skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.poster.avif?t=1771035517\" width=426 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.webm?t=1771035517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3688340/extras/2c29fa29f74506f0d4226bcb781895d4.mp4?t=1771035517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is inspired by the game below:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy</p></li></ul>",
